title: Matisyahu - Akeda (2014) 320kbps
description:
Akeda is the fifth LP from American reggae rapper Matisyahu. The tracks were mainly written while on tour and then recorded at Studio G in Brooklyn, New York with producer Stu Brooks (50 Cent, Norah Jones) and Joe Hamilton (Pretty Lights, Elvis Costello). The album was preceded by the single "Watch the Walls Melt Down."
